- Joe: You could buy a new Bronco for less.
- Sonya: I don't want a new... !

06:13.034 --> 06:16.489
I don't want a new Bronco. I want this one.

06:16.684 --> 06:18.950
Joe: Lady, I... I got good hearing.

06:19.852 --> 06:21.811
Sonya: This mechanic' useless.

