Wade: Well, I've been using him for years.

06:23.780 --> 06:25.350
Sonya: Well, he's very stubborn.

06:26.102 --> 06:28.331
<i>Wade: He is. Hmm.</i>

06:29.613 --> 06:32.492
Sonya: He wants me to junk it.

06:32.864 --> 06:34.572
Wade: Sonya...

06:36.142 --> 06:39.737
it was her car. It is not her.

06:50.575 --> 06:52.339
In any case, could you wrap it up?

06:52.367 --> 06:55.469
- The D.A.'s waiting to prep me.
- (Sonya sighs)

07:14.472 --> 07:16.171
Sonya: Can you get the tape out?

07:16.291 --> 07:17.639
It's stuck.

07:17.759 --> 07:19.654
Joe: That I can do.

07:46.035 --> 07:48.933
Wade: Prosecutor can't get a hold of Marco.

07:48.952 --> 07:50.707
Sonya: Yeah, me neither.

07:52.072 --> 07:54.747
Wade: We need him to show up.

07:55.407 --> 07:57.032
Sonya: Well, I've called him 11 times

07:57.051 --> 07:59.484
and he hasn't called me back, so...

07:59.837 --> 08:01.686
